Yes, Sir. A committee has been set up to advise the Army Council on building questions, including the placing of works contracts and the supervision of works in progress. The members of the committee are:


Mr. J. Jameson, C.B.E. (Chairman);

Mr. M. T. Tudsbery, M.Inst.C.E.;

Mr. C. E. Elcock, F.R.I.B.A.;

Mr. Arthur S. Ainsley.

The committee has already started on its work.
